results.name: Self-inverse permutation of natural numbers induced by the automorphism RotateHandshakes_et_DeepReverse! acting on the parenthesizations encoded by A014486.
comment: This automorphism reflects non-crossing handshakes (the interpretation n of Stanley's exercise 19) over the diagonal that goes through corner at "11 o'clock".
